•	He stated that he doesn’t want to work in South Africa as per his caseworker and the development department.

•	When the caseworker contacted him to advise him that his last rental request was not approved, she encouraged him to return to SANZAF’s development department with respect to employment. 

•	As per the caseworker, Mohamed stated ‘Thank you so much for all the assistance he received from SANZAF’. (22/11/2022).

•	That was the last that SANZAF heard from Mohamed.

I hope that this report provides clarity with respect to the recipient, Mohamed Mtshali.

Shukran

